@extends("layouts.fronted_master")
@section("title", " - Become Member")
@section("content")
<section id="become-member" class="content-section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-8 offset-lg-2">

                <!-- privacy-policy -->
                <div class="become-member" style="text-align: justify;">
                    <div class="title-section">
                        <h1>Become a Member of ETHICS®</h1>
                    </div>
                    <p>Joining ETHICS® is a straightforward process designed to accommodate the diverse needs of potential members. Prospective members can choose between two convenient methods to initiate their membership journey: through the online application system or via email communication.</p>

                    <h2>Online Application System:</h2>
                    <p>The online application system offers a user-friendly platform for prospective members to submit their membership applications efficiently. To join ETHICS® through the <a href="">online application system</a>, individuals or organizations can visit the official ETHICS® website and navigate to the membership section. Here, they will find a dedicated application portal where they can provide essential information, such as contact details, organizational affiliations (if applicable), and a brief overview of their interest in joining ETHICS®. Upon completing the online application form, prospective members can submit their application electronically. The ETHICS® team will then review the application and process it accordingly, ensuring a seamless and timely membership enrollment process.</p>

                    <h2>Email Communication:</h2>
                    <p>Alternatively, individuals or organizations who prefer to join ETHICS® via email communication can reach out to the Director of Member Relations directly at <a href="mailto:membership@ethics.com">membership@ethics.org</a>. By sending an email expressing their interest in becoming a member of ETHICS®, prospective members can initiate the membership enrollment process. The Director of Member Relations will promptly respond to the inquiry, providing guidance on the necessary steps to complete the membership application. Through personalized email communication, prospective members can receive tailored assistance and support throughout the membership enrollment process, ensuring a smooth and hassle-free experience.</p>

                    <p>Regardless of the method chosen, joining ETHICS® offers individuals, traditional publishers, academic institutions, and other stakeholders the opportunity to become part of a global community dedicated to promoting ethical publishing practices. Whether through the online application system or email communication, the membership process is designed to be accessible, efficient, and inclusive, welcoming members from diverse backgrounds and geographic locations. Join ETHICS® today and embark on a journey towards ethical publishing excellence.</p>
                </div>
                <!-- End privacy-policy -->

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
@endsection